Position Limit Needed to Curb Manipulation, CFTC’s Chilton Says

-- B y   B e n   M o s h i n s k y
-- 
2011-10-18T11:03:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-18/position-limit-needed-to-curb-manipulation-cftc-s-chilton-says.html
Limits on the proportion of a market
commodities traders can control are necessary to prevent price
manipulation,  Bart Chilton , a commissioner of the Commodity
Futures Trading Commission, said today.  “I’ve seen the manipulation of markets before,” Chilton
said in an interview with Bloomberg Television today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
